description: Welcome to 588 E 7th Street. This spacious single-family home boasts a thoughtfully renovated first level designed for modern and comfortable living. The first floor is equipped with a stunning gas fireplace, a contemporary kitchen, and a well-lit, cheerful interior. Ascending to the second level, you'll find two generously sized bedrooms and a full bathroom. Continuing upwards to the third floor, a bonus living room, an additional full bathroom, and two large bedrooms complete the layout. For outdoor enthusiasts, the expansive backyard is the perfect setting for entertaining guests and enjoying the outdoors. Schedule your showing to call this place 'home'.
